Era: Era of Creation
Reign: Beginning - Feb.-Mar. 2001
Gazboy, along with Lycia, created 
the FAQ division back in 2000, 
he ran the division for several 
months as Chief with Lycia's help. 
However, Lycia ran away to better 
things on G2001, so Gazboy was 
left to run it alone. A few months 
later, he became very inactive and 
left most of the Chief duties to 
his Asst. Chief, Pozion. Gaz was 
eventually fired by the admins and 
replaced with the Senior Captain, 
ShadowFox.
