Era: Era of Building
Reign: Mar. 2000 - May 2000
ShadowFox took over as Chief
when Gazboy was fired as admin.
Things ran smoothly for her for 
the first month. Then, however,
she became very inactive and 
mean to Graalians seeking help,
not answering questions or yelling
at people who did ask. Lycia, 
FAQ's co-creator, decided to take 
her 'baby' back, illegally. She told
Zorro, the Account Admin, that
Galen had given the go-ahead to 
be FAQ Chief. She was then 
given the Chief postion by Zorro,
thinking it was Galen's wish.
She undid some of SF's work
in FAQ and implimented her own.
After about a week, the admins 
realized she had gotten the 
position illegally and gave it back 
to ShadowFox. Though it was
only a couple of weeks later
that ShadowFox was fired and 
the Chief postion was given to
her Asst. Chief, BloodySin.
